# options / modifiers / flags

attributes / options  - bit-range or variable that contains one or more option / modifiers regions
 the range is named FOO_ATTR

option      - bit-range which contains one from a set of options, with zero as the default
 the range is named FOO_OPT
 the options are named FOO_BAR

modifiers / flags   - bit-range which contains zero or more options from a set
 the range is named FOO_MOD
 the options are named FOO_BAR

